--- !u!114 &389157645
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 389157644}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 829b12bc487898c44ba9bed64d1ca9b3, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  kind: 1
  nextSceneName: Level3
  loadSceneWhenFinished: 1
  onBeforeLoadScene:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  darkIntroSegments:
  - I have been waiting for you for longer than you remember.
  - ' You kept walking forward, but left pieces of yourself behind.'
  - In the rain you no longer ran. In the dark you no longer looked up.
  - I know all your frustration, your pain, your sadness, your silence, your doubt,
    your quiet despair.
  - And now I am here
  - "Not to blame you. Not to stop you. But to remind you\u2014"
  - "You are not broken. You are not lost. You are only\u2026 incomplete."
  - Come find me. Through the thorns. Through the silence. Through the self you buried
    away.
  - This time, do not turn back.
  - "Take my hand. And we will walk forward\u2014 together, into the light."
  introMessage: "Are you still there?\nThe night feels quieter now.\n\nDid you see
    it?\nThat sky you once believed in.\n\nHold on to it.\nWe\u2019re almost there."
  photoSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 2e35864f9212fa142a4538096d0d0963, type: 3}
  transitionParagraphs:
  - So I walked on
  - Not to escape the dark\nBut to face it
  - The forest thinned\nNight settled in\nThe wind moved softly\nSomething in me
    loosened
  - And there I saw her again \nShe looked to the sky\nEyes full of stars.
  - I knew that gaze\nI had buried it.
  - Perhaps nothing was gone\nOnly hidden in the nights I stopped looking up
  - So this time\nI looked again\nto enjoy the starry night again\nto understand
    myself again
  endPhotoSprite: {fileID: 0}
  chapterTitleText: Chapter3      Embracing Sunrise
  chapterTitleFontSize: 96
  endCreditsSegments:
  - Thanks for your playing.
  - Get you get, and be confident
  darkenDuration: 1.2
  brightenDuration: 1.35
